Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come for our \NRomantic Era High Collar Lady to leave the nest,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,as her fate takes a new, unexpected turn. {運命の歯車, a figurative meaning expression in Japanese, not sure about how I could put it better}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She now has to move in with the fiancé someone else picked for her to learn proper etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can stop her any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's worse, Benio is greeted by a\Nmysterious armored warrior on her first visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is just a dream, it's definitely a bad one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the shogunal vassal's daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's this tone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stall! Answer at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're preparing for a festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe an advertisement for a new doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Y-You insolent fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this spear look decorative to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That looked painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the shogunal vassal's daughter, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an enemy of the emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going back to the days \Nof the Meiji Restoration now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels pretty anachronistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a woman won't save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass the judgment on you\Nmyself to rectify the mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You butcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:03.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,500)\c&HEEE5E4&\pos(720,180)\bord0\blur1.5\b1\fs}Episode 7\N{\fs140}Count, Forgive Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, calm down. Come on, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, relax! I'm a good guy, why can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.52,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They wanna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is this Boss calling out for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go-go-go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Make way, make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to calm down, you damn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll skewer you! \NStop running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What else am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I trust this strict count.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio is now being taught to be ladylike,\Nbut I wouldn't expect her to be very dedicated. {/will not exercise enough} {運動不足になっておるかもしれんのう, I don't know if he means this in a positive or a negative way}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, my goal for coming here was\Nto raise hell and get promptly kicked out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But the tables have turned! {/what happened was the opposite}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That warrior doll wouldn't\Nstand a chance if I had a sword! If only...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they have a sword somewhere? \NSword, sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! There's one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll compensate for its size \Nwith my two-handed fencing. {lit: I have confidence in my ittou-ryu with two hands}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in that armor's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! I'm done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Milord! {judging by voice it was grandma ijuuin so im not sure she'll refer to her own husband as milord in english but i really cant think of a better word here}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone say "Milord" right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... could they be referring \Nto this mansion's owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, I wouldn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, only princes, \Ncounts and barons get called that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't suppose this is the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's likely that there could be a count.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As mad as it sounds,\Nthis stuffed samurai doll is... {Boys' May Festival dolls stuffed toy; stuffed animal; plush toy; soft toy; cuddly toy} {/Gatchaman}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,he is Count Ijuuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am Shinobu's grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to meet you, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that this guy is a count...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... M-Milord, hang on. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That girl is out of her\Nmind, treating me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To be fair, it was your own doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world were you\Ntrying to do, dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll never allow a marriage \Nwith the daughter of a shogunal vassal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize. I had no clue that he's a count...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a genuinely good man,\Nbut he's a little headstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"A little headstrong" is\Nquite the understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, you didn't get injured, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey-hey, that's enough!\NShut up and listen, won't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he's a prince or a count,\Nhe was still trying to murder one of his guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was a misundersta—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything ever happens to Boss Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you what\Nthis goldfish tattoo truly means! {he's referring to the tattoo in some way, but I don't understand the second half, he's surely threatening her though}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So crude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Whadja say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you saying to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just an oaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, why are you making such\Na racket with your rickshaw over here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of our sight right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Crud, I'm beaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming here, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly resemble your grandfather, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your thick eyebrows, your sharp lip line,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and your masculine features, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Masculine features?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This stings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, my long-time love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rapid flow of water{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}may get split in two by a stepping stone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it will eventually turn into one again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be finally fulfilled, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My first love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Will the day we marry ever come?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Ah! Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, I'm afraid of dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou isn't a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it so hard to understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boys, you can listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like how you're\Nprotecting the people who live here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou is trying his best to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness! They've never\Nbeen affectionate to strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Impertinent girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:13:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, our world works in mysterious ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Something incredible just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievably, Benio easily\Ntamed Tenmaru and Chimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I'd expect from Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd sense it in her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like dogs are way more\Naccommodating than people here, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Tenmaru, Chimaru, \Nlook after Boss Benio while I'm not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, I'll go away at once. Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, who is that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ushigorou? He's my hen-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. He's my—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Lady Benio's devoted manservant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'm sure I heard him say "Boss."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to make it short...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In Benio's family, they use that word\Ninstead of the usual "Sir," grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, knowing you,\NI didn't expect your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This get-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There he goes again with the snickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I bet you've already\Ncaused some mischief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity that I wasn't there to watch it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity, I'm not an Asakusa\Nspectacle for your amusement! Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to see that you two are\Nalready playing pranks on each other! {assuming she means "you two get along and so act playful" assuming benio's spectacle was a prank on shinobu}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, it's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it wasn't {\i1}that{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, you didn't have to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That guy is such a grandmother's boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be because she brought him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They say older people\Noften spoil their children. {There is a saying that goes, ``An old man is three pennies cheaper.'' A proverb says that a child who is spoiled by his or her grandparents has less human worth than other children, ``having no patience and becoming dependent on others.''; lit: elder's child is 3 mon cheaper, the saying goes - he must be one of that kind}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like that's just the case with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, Ms. Kisaragi is going\Nto assist you all the way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave her to me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the Count is from Kagoshima, \Nwe follow those traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that it's difficult,\Nbut please get used to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach her with\Ngreat attention until the wedding day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood-curdling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, please show Lady Benio her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So your grandfather is from Kagoshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you've already met him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that old-fashioned dotard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep down, he's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a little stubborn \Nand often gets carried away. {lit: takes jokes too far}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's completely unhinged!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He was {\i1}this{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}close to outright \Nspearing me back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He just wanted to intimidate you a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he resent me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem to like \Nthat your ancestors were shogunal vassals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,During the Meiji Restoration, \NSatsuma fought them to the bitter end,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,even though they were both Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That happened moons ago!\NIt's inappropriate to fuss over it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I admit that even I\Ndidn't behave properly at all, still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can picture this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, just stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So, to sum it up, after your grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,bade farewell to my grandfather,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,she met and married your grandfather, Ijuuin,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,who was a samurai from Satsuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they had a son, and so did your grandparents, their promise was passed down to their grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're the chosen ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less, \Nbut let's go easy about it for now. {lit is "let's not worry about it" but that's not something you say about the marriage so idk how to word it"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's now on the Ijuuin family's bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't jump to conclusions yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still not officially married yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi, why are you so battered?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Two enormous lupine dogs attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What about Benio? \NShe didn't get injured, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It ended in a blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Even though\Nthey shredded my clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment they saw the Boss, \Nthey became docile!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, even the Ijuuins could\Nbecome as affectionate to her very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, that can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio went there to\Ntry and break her betrothal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm doubtful about the viability of this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Destiny could already be written.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful...\NThis is just like a foreign princess's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's like a prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that I'm thinking, all of a sudden? {/what the dickens}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also a great panorama from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired, so I'll take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It truly is a marvelous room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate both Shinobu and this house, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I only like my new room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Erm... Dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please dress up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I need to get changed just to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:21:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,These are our rules,\Nso follow them and dress up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get dressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... want to... Just... let me... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was tough, but we made it with style.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just because you forced me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I'm starving now.\NI'd love a good dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll eat all of it and lick the leftovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Western style? What the... \NI don't know these manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know these manners...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever our High Collar Lady goes,\Nit turns into a symphony of laughter and romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't give up.\NDestiny has many things in store!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady,\Nnot knowing Western manners,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is catapulted into a clanking table.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite being on the verge of tears, the kind\NShinobu gives her a glimpse of a sweet dream,{Idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.34,0:23:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,incessantly disrupted by her table mates!{I don't understand}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What will Benio do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady{\i0}:\N"I Won't Weep 'til I Win"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
